Added Debug message to Westpac Code
Xposed Bridge JAR Library is not needed thanks to Gradle Integration
Updated App VersionName and VersionCode to 1.3-BETA1 (4)
Updated Android Support Library.
Enabled MainActivity as Launcher Activity
Added Menu to MainActivity.
Added Layout to hold Views for future use.
Moved MainActivity into new subpackages specifically for Activity's only.
Put xmlns:android XML property on a new line for visual consistency.
Realigned some properties on a new line for visual consistency. New Xposed Description added.
Added an Annotations Dependency for whole project and added ButterKnife Library and some other smaller libraries to the app module.
Made a ContactActivity for contact information.
Copied some XML layout and java code from SuperKiwi
Enabled Contact Me redirection
Added PBomb Logo as drawable
Added AboutActivity
Fixed ContactActivity button binding listener.
Changed App theme though most likely will change in the future.
Added Singleton.
Added Preference Provider for external SharePreferences access.
Added PreferenceFragment to MainActivity so end-user can configure which settings are enabled.
Added Class which holds information on Preferences.
Added Generic Preference Fragment and Activity to load any preference XML dynamically.
Added preference XML files for each application being hooked.
Added proper string values for all preferences and fixed any inconsistent key names.
Gave each NestedPreferenceActivity a meaningful title that is related to the information displayed.
Made the accent colour an Australian green colour to have a colour theme that matches their national colours.
Added Activity Animations.
Removed unnecessary space.
Added Package Names to Common class.
Fixed inconsistent language used.
Added Default SharedPreference file and application installed checks when Activity is created.
Moved static variables to Singleton class.

Added code so the PreferenceFragment can read the SharedPreferences files automatically.
Added debug preference key for future use.
Changed hooks from a static to dynamic by reading the SharedPreference file.

Added Debugging toggle in GUI.
